What kind of sword has that great power?

37
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:37,300
Could it be another sword deity?

38
00:03:40,490 --> 00:03:42,320
That is the Tianzhan Sword.

39
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,280
The first among the top ten famous swords.

40
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,490
How could this be?!

41
00:03:57,080 --> 00:04:01,730
Since Heaven has chosen me, I shall follow Heaven's will.

42
